  <para>
    Load the &layerset; of the currently <link
    linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Graphics_n.Layer.Select">selected</link>
    &layer; into the &layereditor;, opening and raising the
    &layereditor; window if necessary.  The selected &layer; will be
    highlighted and ready to edit in the &layereditor;'s list of <link
    linkend="RegisteredClass-DisplayMethod"><classname>DisplayMethods</classname></link>.
  </para>
  <para>
    In text mode, this command doesn't do anything.  To edit graphics
    &layers; in text mode, use the &layereditor; commands in the <xref
    linkend="MenuItem-OOF.LayerEditor.LayerSet"/> menu.
  </para>

